Package: mlr3db
Title: Data Base Backend for mlr3
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Michel",
           family = "Lang",
           role = c("cre", "aut"),
           email = "michellang@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9754-0393"))
Description: Extends the mlr3 package with a data backend to
    transparently work with data bases. Internally relies on the
    abstraction of `dbplyr`.
